<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-04-18T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-04-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="446" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d446">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic"><gloss type="from">Acting British
                                    consul-general</gloss> to <gloss type="to">United States
                                    legation</gloss>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Tabriz</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-04-18"><hi rend="italic">April 18,
                                1898</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 8.]</seg></opener>
                        <p>Bagdasarian has been handed to-day to me. I shall do needful.</p>
                        <frus:attachment>
                            <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Inclosure 2 in No.
                                    21.—Translation.—Telegrams sent in Turkish.]</seg></opener>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic"><persName type="from">Bagdasarian</persName> to
                                        <gloss type="to">United States Minister</gloss>.</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Salmas</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="hijri gregorian" when="1898-04-09"><hi rend="italic">17th of Zeekadeh, 1315</hi> (<hi rend="italic">9th of April,
                                    1898</hi>)</date>.</dateline>
                                <seg rendition="#left">No. 1.]</seg></opener>
                            <p>By order of the Emir-i-Nizam, I am kept as a prisoner. I beg you to
                                obtain my release.</p>
                        </frus:attachment>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>